ğŸ“º LCD (16x2 in 4-bit mode)
Great choice! Using an I2C LCD with your Arduino calculator simplifies wiring and frees up digital pins. Hereâ€™s everything you need to get started:

ğŸ”Œ I2C LCD Wiring (16x2)
| I2C Pin | Function | Arduino Pin | 
|   GND   | Ground   |     GND     | 
|   VCC   | Power    |      V5     | 
|   SDA   | Data Line|      A4     | 
|   SCL   |Clock Line|      A5     | 

Note: These are standard I2C pins for Arduino Uno. If you're using a different board, the SDA/SCL pins may vary.
